name: Jamesteria

pages.title: Jamesteria
pages.content: Jamesteria (James) is a talented songwriter and singer who I produce and engineer for. We've made quite a collaborations so far including Cadillac Ivory Bone and Taylor Swift covers. A lot more to come soon.

pages.title: Cadilac Ivory Bone
pages.content: Cadilac Ivory Bone was the first official and original production of a pop-rock fusion song. I was in charge of mixing, producing, sound design, and general engineering. Jamesteria wrote and sung the song. Images are in credits to him.

description: Jamesteria (James) is a talented songwriter and singer who has collaborated with me on multiple songs and covers.

name: Pavel Lipski

pages.title: Pavel Lipski
pages.content: Pavel is a talented orchestral producer, songwriter and musician who has mentored me in music production and audio engineering. We made a song together called Midnight and currently working on an upcoming Album.

name: Chamele Listens

pages.title: Chamele Listens
pages.content: Chamele Listens is a multi-genre producer with whom I have collaborated on multiple projects, including the track Bad Apple! Vocaloid Cover, Calydon, as well as mastered their new Memory Album.
